name: Attempt To Communicate
description:
Back in 1981 until early 2000, there was a lot of public telephone in Indonesia. It's become the main need for communication because back in the day, the price of handphones is still high. A lot of stories happened when I use the public telephone. And now the public telephone is just abandoned and waiting to vanish.

Canon EOS 80D
3979 x 5022 pixels
